question: How many districts are there in Kota Bogor, Indonesia?
asked_question_translated: Mitu linnaosa on Kota Bogoris, Indoneesias?
answer: Kota Bogoris, Indoneesias on kuus linnaosa: Bogor Selatan, Bogor Timur, Bogor Utara, Bogor Tengah, Bogor Barat ja Tanah Sareal.
answer_translated_eng: Kota Bogoris, Indoneesias on kuus linnaosa: South Bogor, East Bogor, North Bogor, Central Bogor, West Bogor ja Tanah Sareal.
